songs.title: Zamana Jali
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Yeah, here we go

[Hook: Bohemia]
Ajj kal zamana jali, zamana jali aj kal zamana jali (x4)
Ajj kal de log jali, zamana jali
Mattam te sog jali, zamana jali
Ajj kal umeed jali, zamana jali
Ajj kal di preet jali, zamana jali

[Verse 1: Bohemia]
Par, asli aje vi main ve jiven
Nasli, jeri mere chi shae ve par
Bass nhi, mainu merete main ve
Duniya ch dass nahi bass iko hi main ve
Mere, piche-piche, zamana jali
Jinnu dil ton dua do oh daye gali
Jinnu andhere chon kad ke roshni dhikhao
Ohi andhera dhikhae tuhanu jadon odi bari
Jinnu tijori dikhao ohi kare khali
Jeda phol tore bagh chon oh hi bane mali par
Raja sadaah befikar main kadi dil
Chi duniya da rakheya nai dar
Ae duniya dor badal de kardi nai der
Har sher de haq chi saddah rehndi nai saver
Ajj raaj karain kal jiven ani ni vari
Ajj kal vairi asli, zamana jali

[Hook: Bohemia]
Ajj kal zamana jali, zamana jali ajj kal zamana jali (x2)
Ajj kal de log jali, zamana jali
Mattam te sog jali, zamana jali
Ajj kal umeed jali, zamana jali
Aj kal di preet jali, zamana jali

[Verse 2: Bohemia]
Ajj kal de variyan ton daran main vi
Vairi sadkan te nai oh tech savvy
Excess chi munde twenty four seven
Gal khatt karan text heavy
Payback pinda vicho baithe-baithe
Online worldwide munde kisi nu vi karan hack
Shoni kudi jedi sada mile online ontime
FaceTime mango kehndi next time
Nale ajj kal airports te mainu tang karan
Ve munde border patrol de
Mainu khalaar ke savaal mere to puchan
Mere bag kholan meri jeban tattol de per
Aje vi main hass ke javaab dena
Smuggle kare hash jeda munda onu daat dena
Jhina de siran te appa kali raatan ch firde suraj de chad de
Vi ohna da hi saath dinda
Ajj kal loki labban mere chi kharabi
Mere jamman ton pelan ton mera peo si sharabi per
Hun oh vi deke mainu maa di gali ve khendey
Bete dhyian naal chali zamana jali

[Outro]
Ajj kal zamana jali, zamana jali ajj kal zamana jali (x2)
Ajj kal de log jali, zamana jali
Mattam te sog jali, zamana jali
Ajj kal umeed jali, zamana jali
Ajj kal di preet jali, zamana jali
